          },
          "reviewBody": "Lokseva school is a very good & beautiful school. It has a very big sports ground and Swimming pool. Teachers quality is very good. Shubhrata mam is a great teacher. Mamta mam & Gouri joshi mam teaches very well. I love this school. School conducts various activities for students apart from studies. I am the 1st year student.",
